I appreciate all your help Ursula. Although I&#39;d love to have the 3, the package would probably be better for me.

I&#39;ve bought things from China in the past, and although it&#39;s a long wait, the stuff is usually good. But once I got a portable cd writer, and they sent me the case only. When I told them they advertised it in the title as a writer, they said that was just keywords. So I lost money on that, and am now cautious about buying from China. I waited over 2 months for something that wasn&#39;t even what I purchased. Grrrr....

~Draiga

